  "texts": [
    "Mindfulness Attention Awareness Scale (MAAS):",
    "The Mindful Attention Awareness Scale is a questionnaire used to assess an individual's tendency to be mindful and aware of their thoughts and emotions without being overly reactive or overwhelmed by them.",
    "It aims to gauge one's overall level of mindfulness and ability to remain present in the moment.",
    "Higher scores on the MAAS indicate a stronger capacity for mindfulness and present-moment attention.",
    "The MAAS normally consists of 15 items."
  ],
